'''Personal rocket packs''' are small [[Rocket pack/Legends|rocket packs]], with many made by [[Zim Systems]]. [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]] owned two rocket packs: a [[JT-12 jetpack/Legends|Merr-Sonn JT-12]] and a [[Z-6 jetpack/Legends|Mitrinomon Z-6]], a model later used by his [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] son [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]].

